{"tid":392424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蓮蓉幾時出殯？","createTime":"2017-09-08T13:14:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-08T13:31:17.000Z","uid":56051,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dad808dd4b90ba4a4d8ce9e781fd031bca259041","tid":392424,"uid":56051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T13:14:18.000Z","msg":"一個高官喪子，心情的難受可以想像，由此引起的爭論、罵戰、對立，只會令痛者更痛，無日無之。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">修補撕裂的最佳方法，愚以為是大家留意局長兒子大喪的日子，到時召集各派到場殯喪。</span></strong>屆時藍絲、黃絲、本土、內地生、中聯辦、習派、江派、林特首、曾特首、梁特首，齊齊到場，萬人空巷，不分你我，痛哭流涕。無限的同理心和振動宇宙的人道大愛蓋過分歧與仇恨。這就是壞事變好事，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">喪事變喜事，</span></strong>人神共賀了。Peter在天之靈也覺安慰，祖國母親也一定會興奮難止！"},{"pid":"4b602cdc62bdbc8c18a7ac3fd5bea5ed11c0d622","tid":392424,"uid":54264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T13:17:16.000Z","msg":"白事當紅事辦有支那特色<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13346f932ae1066cbe1ae0b38a575c8849f12da6","tid":392424,"uid":56051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T13:18:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有請小鳳姐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a hr